10 Finally, be strong in the Lord and in his mighty power. 11 Put on the full armor of God, so that you can take your stand against the devil’s schemes. 12 For our struggle is not against flesh and blood, but against the rulers, against the authorities, against the powers of this dark world and against the spiritual forces of evil in the heavenly realms. 13 Therefore put on the full armor of God, so that when the day of evil comes, you may be able to stand your ground, and after you have done everything, to stand. 14 Stand firm then, with the belt of truth buckled around your waist, with the breastplate of righteousness in place, 15 and with your feet fitted with the readiness that comes from the gospel of peace. 16 In addition to all this, take up the shield of faith, with which you can extinguish all the flaming arrows of the evil one. 17 Take the helmet of salvation and the sword of the Spirit, which is the word of God.

18 And pray in the Spirit on all occasions with all kinds of prayers and requests. With this in mind, be alert and always keep on praying for all the Lord’s people.

I'm going to collect my thoughts and repost.  I removed my comments and posts from today that offended the redditors, initially thinking I had said something that made a lot of you pissed off at me, and yes maybe that's cowardly but I don't want to piss you guys off, cmon now.

Then I realized it was totally artificial downvoting, looking at past comments, I was like whoa...this consistent downvoting goes on forever... seems the script doesn't touch comments whose updoots are higher than usual, it only downvoted comments people didn't care about (usually stuck at 1, right?)  so it looks worse.

I was trying to figure out what did it, and I am QUITE SURE it was the post where I said that ICE should be in Witness protection, given false identities only known to the agency that's running the program; and then they could go maskless

I assume this it the one the redditors here really didn't like.  I don't think they are so industrious to coordinate an attack on me.  I think its one person with a script and a little anti-ICE botfarm that targetted me.

Anyway, feel free to call me a faggot or narcissist or whatever  ("no those downvotes are real, you just suck and your ideas are bad!") for doing a self post on this, that ultimately doesn't mean anything to you, unless you care about other people on the site being attacked by redditors

The one that got me was D-Frens.  It was pepe version of falling down

I know that fuckin' comment is gold you guys.  It's gold and you know it.
